title: Mickey Factz - #StoreRunner (TRU FOE DISS)
description:
Directed by Mr Good Evening

Mickey Factz ends the trilogy with a scathing diss entitled #STORERUNNER 
The story goes Aye Noun paid Tru Foe to diss Mickey Factz and Mickey proceeded to write 3 songs in under 20 hours from 2 am to 7 pm. Mind you he slept from 7 am to 11 am. So its really 16 hours. Anyway, Factz being the mc he is channeled his anger into one of the most catchiest and creative diss records to date. Long Live Lyricism.

title: "Donald's Sewage Stream" - Marsh Family adapt "Islands in the Stream" by Dolly Parton & Kenny Rogers
description:
â€œIslands in the Streamâ€ was written by the Bee Gees, named after an Ernest Hemingway novel, and first intended for Diana Ross â€¦ but it found its most famous home in the epic country rendition released by Kenny Rogers and Dolly Parton in 1983 which was Dollyâ€™s second number one hit â€“ knocking Bonnie Tylerâ€™s â€œTotal Eclipse of the Heartâ€ off the top spot! 

We had planned to do a cover of it to mark Dollyâ€™s 80th birthday earlier this week. But with the bizarre episodes engineered by Donald Trump and some of his despicable false claims about NATO and track records dominating headlines this week, we determined to create a parody reflecting on his increasingly rambling, drivelling, narcissistic, and palpably untrue speeches â€“ including notably the one he gave at Davos as he climbed down (for now) from his bullying of Greenland (not Iceland, as in the clip). 

For the facts Trump got wrong and the sources used:
- ABC News: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hDgfOdEJyZE
- Trump Davos speech: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qo2-q4AFh_g
- Fact checks of it: https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/c301jgd1qj6o, https://edition.cnn.com/2026/01/21/politics/trump-davos-nato-greenland-fact-check

*Update 12 hours after upload: thanks for helpful people adding to our fact checking, and reminding that although Trump â€œtaunted men who served as soldiersâ€ there were also many female service people and sadly casualties in the Afghanistan operation.

LYRICS 

How come when he gets up every speech drones on?
He sets out to lecture with his facts all wrong 
Heâ€™s gone soft inside 
There is nothing going on!

Someoneâ€™s autocue-ing but heâ€™s unrestrained  
They must wonder â€œCanâ€™t he read the pane?â€
Every speech falls apart
Ego-spewing marathons

Audiences try
Kind of hide their trepidation
Knowing Trumpâ€™s showâ€™in real deterioration
They smile as he blathers: â€œuh-huh!â€
Making up all his numbers, â€œuh-huh!â€

Donaldâ€™s sewage stream
Verbal salad bar
Someone intervene!
You can see heâ€™s wrong
Ailing mentally
In his made-up world
Where he just lies for an hour, uh-huh!
From one subject to another, uh-huh!

Whistleâ€™s going choo-choo yet the trainâ€™s done gone
Gibbering and waffling but the lights ainâ€™t on
So he just talks all this shite
Slowly losing sight of the real things

Now it can happen often that he slurs and shouts
Doing impressions as he gurns and pouts 
And the message is clear:
This must be the year for dementing

No more alibis
Heâ€™s not wily, quirky, clever â€¦ 
His grasp of world events
Is just a toddlerâ€™s
He canâ€™t hide it forever â€“ nuh-huh
Bigging up his dystopia, nuh-huh

Donaldâ€™s sewage stream
That has gone too far
Veterans now demeaned
Getting history wrong
Making mockery
In his latest slur
Of how we fought with each other, huh-uh
Taunting men who served as soldiers, huh-uh

So debased
Oh defames their memory

Wizened tangerine
Bogus and bizarre
Always venting spleen
Like King *senile* Kong
Fade away now please
From our media
So we can talk to each other, uh-huh
Without felons taking over, uh-huh
